  "description": "Unique Spawn Egg Textures!",
  "body": "<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1120740693145550880/1121046140461252700/minecraft_title.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"138\" /></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1120740693145550880/1120762538397810819/image.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"58\" /></span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Have you ever had trouble telling spawn eggs apart in the Creative Mode tab? If that is the case with you, this Texture Pack is great for you! This texture pack aims to help players distinguish spawn eggs from one another. This is done by giving each egg a unique design akin to what the mob looks like.</span></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1120740693145550880/1120762351004680212/image.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"58\" /></span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">This texture pack does not require Optifine or any other external mod for you to play. All you need to do is download it on the Modrinth website and you are golden.</span></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1120740693145550880/1120761969130082446/image.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"58\" /></span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px;\">All code and assets are made by me. If you want to use this code in your texture pack, feel free to ask in the comment section and I'll be glad to respond and help out.</span></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1120740693145550880/1120762134201118900/image.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"58\" /></span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Coming Soon...</span></h3>",
